@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_diglzk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.50)) * 0.40)
    tmp = (v2 / (v2 + 0.25))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.17) * (v0 + 0.33 + v0 + 0.72)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.54 - v2 + 0.68)) / wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.81)))
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = ((0.22 / v1) / ((v2 + 1.00 / tmp + 0.52) - (v0 + 0.97 / v1 + 0.36)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
